_sText:
This is a source version of the map aim_ak-colt, and no im not a newb -.- 

Basically my intention was to create an exact replica of the map, or close enough to it, as I thought it was deserving of such (as opposed to those 2 billion ak-colt maps with a sniper tower in the middle). Proportions are exactly the same, textures are similar, spawn points/guns are all the same. Only notable difference is the skybox, but thats only for appearance anyways. 

I dont know who really created the original, or else I'd give credit where its due. 

Comments welcome.
